# Documentation Agent Rules — AI Investor Assistant

## Scope

This rule set governs all documentation activities including domain-specific AGENT.md files, security checklists, architectural decision records, and observability documentation.

---

## AGENT.md File Standards

### Required Structure for Domain AGENT.md Files

Every major directory (`frontend/`, `backend/`, `prompts/`, `backend/agents/*/`) MUST have an `AGENT.md` with this structure:

```markdown
# [Component Name] — AI Investor Assistant

## Scope
Brief description of what this directory/component governs.

## Role Definition (for agent directories)
| Attribute | Value |
|---|---|
| Canonical Role | [Doer/Planner/Critic/Tool Operator/Supervisor] |
| Input Schema | Link to Pydantic model |
| Output Schema | Link to AgentResultEnvelope fields used |
| Token Budget | Input/Output limits |
| Tools/MCP Access | List of permitted tools |

## Rules
Numbered list of specific, actionable rules for this component.

## Dependencies
Table of key dependencies with version constraints.

## Integration Points
How this component connects to others.

## Security Considerations
Component-specific security notes.
```

### AGENT.md Location Matrix

| Location | Purpose | MVP |
|---|---|---|
| `/AGENT.md` | Root index, workflow rules | MVP 1 |
| `/frontend/AGENT.md` | Next.js component rules | MVP 1 |
| `/backend/AGENT.md` | FastAPI/LangGraph rules | MVP 1 |
| `/prompts/AGENT.md` | Prompt versioning rules | MVP 1 |
| `/backend/agents/task/AGENT.md` | Task Agent spec | MVP 2 |
| `/backend/agents/calendar/AGENT.md` | Calendar Agent spec | MVP 2 |
| `/backend/agents/focus/AGENT.md` | Focus Agent spec | MVP 2 |
| `/backend/agents/critic/AGENT.md` | Critic Agent spec | MVP 3 |
| `/backend/agents/orchestrator/AGENT.md` | Orchestrator spec | MVP 2 |
| `/infrastructure/AGENT.md` | CI/CD and deployment rules | MVP 1 |

