## Observability Documentation Standards

### docs/OBSERVABILITY.md Requirements

1. **Metrics Registry** — All custom metrics with descriptions
2. **Trace Propagation** — How trace_id flows through the system
3. **Alert Rules** — Prometheus/Grafana alert definitions
4. **SLOs** — Service Level Objectives with error budgets
5. **Dashboard Links** — References to monitoring dashboards

### Metrics Documentation Format

```markdown
## Custom Metrics Registry

| Metric Name | Type | Labels | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `briefing_generation_duration_seconds` | Histogram | `status`, `agent` | Time to generate briefing |
| `llm_tokens_used_total` | Counter | `model`, `agent` | Tokens consumed by LLM calls |
| `mcp_call_duration_seconds` | Histogram | `server`, `tool` | MCP tool call latency |
| `dlq_events_total` | Counter | `reason`, `agent` | Dead letter queue entries |
```

